{"tid":841943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【台灣最美風景】疑失智台婦遭繩綑頸綁陽台　媳婦：家中無人時免生意外　警：不涉虐待","createTime":"2018-09-30T01:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T02:07:46.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8c9fb7d2291a3b3a3b6ad2532e9a761e632000d7","tid":841943,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T01:55:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180929/s00004/716a10c9aa91e2551d9a492ccdede294.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180929%2Fs00004%2F716a10c9aa91e2551d9a492ccdede294.jpg&h=a1bef197&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣彰化縣鹿港疑發生虐老事件。有網民在多個fb群組上傳圖文，亦有影片顯示，一名年紀老邁的婦人疑遭媳婦以繩索綑頸，綁在一處大樓住戶的陽台上，彰化縣社會處及鹿港警方今午派人到場了解。警方表示，該名70多歲老婦經常失禁和自殘等，媳婦有事出門時便會將婆婆綁在陽台，免生意外。<br />\n<br />\n有台灣網民在fb上傳影片，文中指自己在曬衣服時，經常看到一個較低層住戶的陽台，有老婦被媳婦綁在陽台上，曾前往關心卻被罵了一頓，坦言「綁自己媽媽還有天理嗎？」另一照片則看到老婦全身赤裸，坐在陽台的椅子上。帖文隨即在網上引起廣泛討論，網民一面倒批評老婦的家人「沒良心」。<br />\n<br />\n彰化縣社會處與鹿港警方均表示未接獲通報，但已派人趕到現場了解，初步發現老婦失智、經常失禁和重聽等，媳婦將她綁在陽台上是方便照顧，並非虐待。另有台灣傳媒引述「鹿港偵查隊」人員指出，涉事媳婦解釋，只要她出門時，怕老人家在家中做出危險的事，才會將她綁起來。"},{"pid":"8e203a699220842294e2370187e8924303fc5d79","tid":841943,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T01:58:20.000Z","msg":"做人做到咁 生存落去仲有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb8316ccb563280c7c4a4352dde408afb13a77ab","tid":841943,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8e203a699220842294e2370187e8924303fc5d79","tid":841943,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T01:58:20.000Z","msg":"做人做到咁 生存落去仲有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T02:00:26.000Z","msg":"窮姐 有錢味請工人照顧"},{"pid":"714d2596cbcc6535aeb1506038d60d22e04f9f08","tid":841943,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bb8316ccb563280c7c4a4352dde408afb13a77ab","tid":841943,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8e203a699220842294e2370187e8924303fc5d79","tid":841943,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T01:58:20.000Z","msg":"做人做到咁 生存落去仲有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T02:00:26.000Z","msg":"窮姐 有錢味請工人照顧"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T02:00:59.000Z","msg":"工人一樣會虐待<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6acbc96a16c6480b8b0920c086d3d42f08d15d2","tid":841943,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T02:01:10.000Z","msg":"咁倒不如整個籠圍鳩住佢當寵物養好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋做人做到咁,又失智又自殘搞到要比人綁,真係寧願死撚左佢算<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9653b0450c9691f6852018c054314f7725a67d58","tid":841943,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"714d2596cbcc6535aeb1506038d60d22e04f9f08","tid":841943,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bb8316ccb563280c7c4a4352dde408afb13a77ab","tid":841943,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8e203a699220842294e2370187e8924303fc5d79","tid":841943,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T01:58:20.000Z","msg":"做人做到咁 生存落去仲有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T02:00:26.000Z","msg":"窮姐 有錢味請工人照顧"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T02:00:59.000Z","msg":"工人一樣會虐待<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T02:02:26.000Z","msg":"有錢唔會解決唔到啦"},{"pid":"3681c9db1bc754dbb725590c1bf9b2c6b3f282bd","tid":841943,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9653b0450c9691f6852018c054314f7725a67d58","tid":841943,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"714d2596cbcc6535aeb1506038d60d22e04f9f08","tid":841943,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"